name: F35® Lightning II®
description: Is a family of single-seat, single-engine, fifth generation multirole fighters that are designed to perform ground attack, reconnaissance, and air defense missions with stealth capability. The F-35® has three main models; the F-35A® employs conventional takeoff and landing, the F-35B® will be used for short take-off and vertical-landings, and the F-35C® will be carrier-based. The F-35® models are intended to provide the bulk of tactical airpower for the U.S. Air Force, Marine Corps and Navy over the coming decades.
